<br>
You can bandage hidden and /or  inv.<br>
<br>
You can bind to your max [50% or 70%]  THEN take off all your HP gear bandage some and more THEN put it all back on. DO NOT remove hp items when low in health as you CAN kill yourself [i.e. if you have 100 HP's and remove 2  rings that give you 65HP each You will die]<br>
